# ğŸ® GameTimeConverter - Game Time Converter Tool (English)

## ğŸ“Œ Introduction
GameTimeConverter is a **Windows application** that converts **game time (EGT, UTC-2) into Taipei Time (TST, UTC+8) and New York Time (EST/EDT, UTC-5/UTC-4).**

ğŸ”¹ **Key Features**
- ğŸ® **Game Time Conversion**: Converts **EGT (UTC-2)** into **TST (UTC+8)** and **New York Time**.
- â³ **Easy Input**: Enter time using **`yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm`** format.

